flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Historical sales data availability in SAP S/4HANA.]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers - Extract historical sales data from SAP S/4HANA.]
  N1 --> N2[Cortex: Data Quality & Validation - Cleanse and validate historical sales data.]
  N2 --> N3[Cortex: Cortex Auto Forecast - Develop and refine time-series forecasting models.]
  N3 --> N4[Cortex: AutoML - Perform regression analysis on key influencing variables.]
  N4 --> N5{PB: Remote Functions - Deploy ML-based demand prediction models.}
  N5 -->|Primary| N6[PB: Cortex Monitoring - Monitor and measure forecast accuracy.]
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Improved forecast accuracy leading to reduced COGS and working capital, aligned production and procurement with real-time demand signals.]
  N5 -->|Forecast accuracy below threshold| B1[Retrain models with updated data.]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Improved forecast accuracy.]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N5 -->|Significant changes in demand drivers| B2[Adjust model features and retrain.]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Enhanced model adaptability to new conditions.]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N5 -->|Data quality issues detected| B3[Exclude affected data or cleanse before retraining.]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Reliable model predictions based on clean data.]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]